what:	Spot o' Conf
where:  https://chiselapp.com/user/stwo/repository/spotoconf
who:	Stuart Cassoff <stwo@users.sourceforge.net>
why:	Tcl/Jim extension architecture.
when:	Spring 2018
need:	Tcl 8.6


Spot o' Conf:
  Is a configure and build system for Tcl and Jim extensions.
  Was inspired by TEA.
  Can build binary or script-only extensions for Tcl or Jim.
  Can build build/install documentation and examples.
  Can run tests and make distribution files.
